      "text": "With those whips.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 271,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them pretend they were going to hurt us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 271,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they pretend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 272,
